{"article_id":"XpVigkraQjREBq1O","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Story highlights","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"House leaders say","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"the full chamber could vote on contempt next week","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"A House committee recommends a contempt citation against Attorney General Holder","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"Democrats call the contempt measure unfair and an election year witch hunt","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"At issue are documents","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"the panel seeks on the botched Fast and Furious gun-running sting","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"Voting on strictly partisan lines ,","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"a House committee recommended Wednesday","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"that Attorney General Eric Holder be cited for contempt of Congress","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"for failing to turn over documents","depth":10},{"id":11,"text":"relating to the botched Fast and Furious weapons sting operation .","depth":10},{"id":12,"text":"The vote ended an extraordinary daylong hearing","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"that took place","depth":10},{"id":14,"text":"after President Barack Obama asserted executive privilege over some documents","depth":11},{"id":15,"text":"sought by the panel","depth":12},{"id":16,"text":"investigating Fast and Furious .","depth":12},{"id":17,"text":"The White House move means the Department of Justice can withhold some of the documents .","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"The committee measure now goes to the full House for consideration ,","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"expected next week ,","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"of what would be an unprecedented action","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"-- Congress holding a sitting attorney general in contempt .","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"`` Unless the attorney general re-evaluates his choice","depth":12},{"id":23,"text":"and supplies the promised documents ,","depth":12},{"id":24,"text":"the House will vote to hold him in contempt next week , ''","depth":11},{"id":25,"text":"said a statement by the chamber 's Republican leaders .","depth":10},{"id":26,"text":"`` If , however , Attorney General Holder produces these documents prior to the scheduled vote ,","depth":10},{"id":27,"text":"we will give the","depth":13},{"id":28,"text":"( committee )","depth":13},{"id":29,"text":"an opportunity","depth":12},{"id":30,"text":"to review in hopes","depth":12},{"id":31,"text":"of resolving this issue . ''","depth":12},{"id":32,"text":"All 23 Republicans on the House Oversight and Government Reform Committee supported the contempt measure ,","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"while the 17 Democrats opposed it ,","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"reflecting the deep political divide on the issue .","depth":10},{"id":35,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":11},{"id":36,"text":"DNC chair :","depth":12},{"id":37,"text":"GOP witch hunt on Holder","depth":12},{"id":38,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"MUST WATCH DNC chair :","depth":11},{"id":40,"text":"GOP witch hunt on Holder","depth":11},{"id":41,"text":"05:00","depth":10},{"id":42,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":12},{"id":43,"text":"Obama invokes executive privilege","depth":12},{"id":44,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":11},{"id":45,"text":"MUST WATCH","depth":12},{"id":46,"text":"Obama invokes executive privilege","depth":12},{"id":47,"text":"06:34","depth":11},{"id":48,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"Congressman :","depth":11},{"id":50,"text":"I believe Holder","depth":11},{"id":51,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":9},{"id":52,"text":"MUST WATCH","depth":11},{"id":53,"text":"Congressman :","depth":12},{"id":54,"text":"I believe Holder","depth":12},{"id":55,"text":"03:39","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":9},{"id":57,"text":"A brief history of 'Fast and Furious '","depth":10},{"id":58,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":11},{"id":59,"text":"MUST WATCH","depth":12},{"id":60,"text":"A brief history of 'Fast and Furious ' 03:01","depth":12},{"id":61,"text":"Committee chairman Rep. Darrell Issa , R-California , refused to put off consideration of the measure ,","depth":11},{"id":62,"text":"saying","depth":12},{"id":63,"text":"the White House assertion of executive privilege `` falls short '' of any reason","depth":13},{"id":64,"text":"to delay the hearing .","depth":13},{"id":65,"text":"However , Issa said after the hearing","depth":11},{"id":66,"text":"that he believes","depth":12},{"id":67,"text":"a settlement","depth":14},{"id":68,"text":"to avoid an unprecedented contempt vote in the House","depth":14},{"id":69,"text":"is `` in the best interest of the Justice Department , Congress and those most directly affected by Operation Fast and Furious . ''","depth":13},{"id":70,"text":"In a statement later Wednesday , Holder called Issa 's decision","depth":12},{"id":71,"text":"to hold the vote","depth":12},{"id":72,"text":"`` an election-year tactic '' and `` an extraordinary , unprecedented and entirely unnecessary action ,","depth":12},{"id":73,"text":"intended to provoke an avoidable conflict between Congress and the executive branch . ''","depth":12},{"id":74,"text":"The committee 's top Democrat , Rep. Elijah Cummings of Maryland , accused Issa of setting an `` impossible standard '' for Holder","depth":12},{"id":75,"text":"by initially demanding documents","depth":13},{"id":76,"text":"the attorney general is legally prohibited from providing .","depth":13},{"id":77,"text":"Now Issa has `` no interest","depth":13},{"id":78,"text":"in resolving '' the dispute with Holder ,","depth":13},{"id":79,"text":"Cummings said .","depth":12},{"id":80,"text":"Wednesday 's developments further heightened the drama of a high-profile showdown between Issa and Holder over the Fast and Furious program","depth":9},{"id":81,"text":"that dates back to subpoenas","depth":10},{"id":82,"text":"issued by the House committee last year .","depth":10},{"id":83,"text":"The Bureau of Alcohol , Tobacco , Firearms and Explosives launched Operation Fast and Furious out of Arizona","depth":11},{"id":84,"text":"to track weapon purchases by Mexican drug cartels .","depth":11},{"id":85,"text":"However , it lost track of more than 1,000 firearms","depth":12},{"id":86,"text":"that the agency had allowed straw buyers to carry across the border ,","depth":12},{"id":87,"text":"and two of the lost weapons turned up at the scene of the 2010 killing of U.S. Border Patrol agent Brian Terry .","depth":11},{"id":88,"text":"Issa 's committee is specifically seeking documents","depth":11},{"id":89,"text":"that show","depth":12},{"id":90,"text":"why the Department of Justice decided to withdraw as inaccurate a February 2011 letter","depth":14},{"id":91,"text":"sent to Congress","depth":14},{"id":92,"text":"that said","depth":14},{"id":93,"text":"top officials had only recently learned about Fast and Furious .","depth":14},{"id":94,"text":"CNN senior political analyst and former presidential adviser David Gergen said","depth":14},{"id":95,"text":"such dusts-ups are usually resolved by political negotiations.","depth":14},{"id":96,"text":"That 's not been the case here .","depth":13},{"id":97,"text":"`` For a lot of Americans","depth":15},{"id":98,"text":"who do n't understand the complexities","depth":16},{"id":99,"text":"and really do n't care about the complexity of this ,","depth":16},{"id":100,"text":"it is one more illustration ...","depth":15},{"id":101,"text":"that Washington is broken , ''","depth":15},{"id":102,"text":"Gergen said .","depth":13},{"id":103,"text":"But the impasse also shows something about Holder 's resolve ,","depth":12},{"id":104,"text":"he told `` John King USA . '' `` He 's stiffened his spine , ''","depth":14},{"id":105,"text":"Gergen said .","depth":14},{"id":106,"text":"`` He has been under pressure to resign from some quarters in the Republican Party .","depth":14},{"id":107,"text":"He ai n't going anywhere . ''","depth":14},{"id":108,"text":"Now the question is whether a settlement can be reached before the House vote .","depth":9},{"id":109,"text":"If the House finds Holder in contempt ,","depth":13},{"id":110,"text":"it is unlikely he will be prosecuted for criminal contempt ,","depth":13},{"id":111,"text":"according to Alan Morrison , associated dean at George Washington University Law School .","depth":12},{"id":112,"text":"`` It would look like terrible overreaching to go for criminal contempt , ''","depth":12},{"id":113,"text":"Morrison said ,","depth":13},{"id":114,"text":"which carries a penalty of $ 1,000 and up to one year in prison .","depth":13},{"id":115,"text":"Instead ,","depth":12},{"id":116,"text":"Morrison said ,","depth":12},{"id":117,"text":"it is more likely the House would pursue civil prosecution in federal court .","depth":11},{"id":118,"text":"The House committee vote came more than six hours after notice","depth":6},{"id":119,"text":"that Obama had asserted executive privilege .","depth":6},{"id":120,"text":"In a letter to Obama","depth":10},{"id":121,"text":"seeking that action ,","depth":10},{"id":122,"text":"Holder said","depth":9},{"id":123,"text":"the documents involved related to the Justice Department 's `` response to congressional oversight and related media inquiries , ''","depth":9},{"id":124,"text":"and that release of internal executive branch documents would have `` significant , damaging consequences . ''","depth":9},{"id":125,"text":"Holder also said","depth":8},{"id":126,"text":"releasing the documents would `` inhibit the candor of executive branch deliberations in the future","depth":9},{"id":127,"text":"and significantly impair the ability of the executive branch","depth":10},{"id":128,"text":"to respond independently and effectively to congressional oversight . ''","depth":10},{"id":129,"text":"Holder said","depth":8},{"id":130,"text":"he offered to turn over some of the documents","depth":10},{"id":131,"text":"sought by Issa","depth":10},{"id":132,"text":"when they met Tuesday in a final effort","depth":10},{"id":133,"text":"to resolve the dispute before Wednesday 's hearing .","depth":10},{"id":134,"text":"Issa , however , said","depth":8},{"id":135,"text":"Holder put unreasonable conditions on his offer .","depth":8},{"id":136,"text":"In a letter to Issa after Tuesday 's meeting , Deputy Attorney General James Cole reiterated Holder 's position","depth":7},{"id":137,"text":"that the documents would show","depth":8},{"id":138,"text":"Holder had nothing to hide about his role in Fast and Furious .","depth":8},{"id":139,"text":"Cole noted","depth":8},{"id":140,"text":"that the lone point of dispute was whether the February 4 , 2011 , letter was part of a broader effort","depth":9},{"id":141,"text":"to obstruct a congressional investigation .","depth":9},{"id":142,"text":"`` The answer to that question is an emphatic 'no ,","depth":9},{"id":143,"text":"' and we have offered the committee the opportunity","depth":10},{"id":144,"text":"to satisfy itself","depth":11},{"id":145,"text":"that that is so , ''","depth":11},{"id":146,"text":"Cole wrote .","depth":8},{"id":147,"text":"The department says","depth":6},{"id":148,"text":"it already has handed over more than 7,000 pages of records to House investigators","depth":7},{"id":149,"text":"and that the remaining material","depth":9},{"id":150,"text":"Issa wants","depth":9},{"id":151,"text":"could jeopardize criminal prosecutions .","depth":8},{"id":152,"text":"Issa and other Republicans on the panel mentioned Brian Terry 's death by name","depth":6},{"id":153,"text":"in accusing Holder and the Justice Department of trying to stonewall the investigation of what happened .","depth":6},{"id":154,"text":"`` The Department of Justice has fought this investigation every step of the way , ''","depth":7},{"id":155,"text":"Issa said .","depth":7},{"id":156,"text":"`` At the heart of the congressional investigation into Operation Fast and Furious are disastrous consequences :","depth":8},{"id":157,"text":"a murdered Border Patrol Agent , his grieving family","depth":10},{"id":158,"text":"seeking answers ,","depth":10},{"id":159,"text":"countless deaths in Mexico , and the souring effect on our relationship with Mexico , ''","depth":9},{"id":160,"text":"Issa said in a statement .","depth":7},{"id":161,"text":"`` Congress has not just a right","depth":5},{"id":162,"text":"but an obligation","depth":6},{"id":163,"text":"to do all","depth":8},{"id":164,"text":"that it can","depth":8},{"id":165,"text":"to uncover exactly what happened","depth":8},{"id":166,"text":"and ensure","depth":9},{"id":167,"text":"that it never occurs again. ``","depth":9},{"id":168,"text":"Terry 's family issued a statement Wednesday","depth":7},{"id":169,"text":"that called for all of the documents","depth":9},{"id":170,"text":"sought by the committee","depth":9},{"id":171,"text":"to be turned over .","depth":8},{"id":172,"text":"`` Our son lost his life","depth":9},{"id":173,"text":"protecting this nation ,","depth":9},{"id":174,"text":"and it is very disappointing that we are now faced with an administration","depth":9},{"id":175,"text":"that seems more concerned with protecting themselves","depth":10},{"id":176,"text":"rather than revealing the truth behind Operation Fast and Furious , ''","depth":10},{"id":177,"text":"the statement said .","depth":7},{"id":178,"text":"The mother of another federal agent said Wednesday","depth":7},{"id":179,"text":"she wants to know the `` full truth '' about his death .","depth":7},{"id":180,"text":"Immigration and Customs Enforcement Agent Jaime Zapata ,","depth":10},{"id":181,"text":"who was working for the United States in Mexico ,","depth":10},{"id":182,"text":"was murdered in February 2011","depth":10},{"id":183,"text":"when his vehicle was ambushed on a highway between Mexico City and Monterrey .","depth":10},{"id":184,"text":"Sen. John Cornyn , R-Texas , last year said","depth":10},{"id":185,"text":"he wanted to know","depth":11},{"id":186,"text":"if a Texas-based `` gun walking '' program may have played a role in Zapata 's murder .","depth":11},{"id":187,"text":"He said","depth":10},{"id":188,"text":"one of the weapons","depth":12},{"id":189,"text":"used in the slaying","depth":12},{"id":190,"text":"was allegedly purchased in Texas","depth":12},{"id":191,"text":"and trafficked to Mexico .","depth":12},{"id":192,"text":"`` Unfortunately , the situation","depth":11},{"id":193,"text":"regarding Fast and Furious as well as other gun-walking operations has been something","depth":11},{"id":194,"text":"that has damaged the lives of many , ''","depth":10},{"id":195,"text":"Zapata 's mother , Mary , said in a statement .","depth":9},{"id":196,"text":"`` I would have hoped","depth":10},{"id":197,"text":"that transparency would have been a priority","depth":10},{"id":198,"text":"so that we , like so many others , could get some answers . ''","depth":9},{"id":199,"text":"The Tuesday meeting between Issa and Holder amounted to little more than a reiteration of the positions","depth":7},{"id":200,"text":"the two staked out in an exchange of letters the previous week .","depth":7},{"id":201,"text":"`` Any claims","depth":11},{"id":202,"text":"that the Justice Department has been unresponsive to requests for information","depth":11},{"id":203,"text":"are untrue , ''","depth":10},{"id":204,"text":"Holder said ,","depth":9},{"id":205,"text":"noting","depth":9},{"id":206,"text":"he shut Fast and Furious down .","depth":9},{"id":207,"text":"The subpoenas","depth":12},{"id":208,"text":"issued last year","depth":12},{"id":209,"text":"originally cited a broad array of documents ,","depth":11},{"id":210,"text":"including wiretap requests and other materials","depth":11},{"id":211,"text":"involving confidential sources","depth":12},{"id":212,"text":"that","depth":14},{"id":213,"text":"Holder argued","depth":14},{"id":214,"text":"he was prevented by law from supplying .","depth":13},{"id":215,"text":"Issa narrowed the request in negotiations with Holder in recent weeks .","depth":9},{"id":216,"text":"Democrats argued","depth":9},{"id":217,"text":"the documents","depth":12},{"id":218,"text":"demanded by Issa","depth":12},{"id":219,"text":"related to internal discussions","depth":12},{"id":220,"text":"about responding to the Fast and Furious investigation ,","depth":12},{"id":221,"text":"rather than the committee 's intended purpose","depth":11},{"id":222,"text":"of finding out","depth":12},{"id":223,"text":"who authorized the failed program .","depth":12},{"id":224,"text":"The party-line division in the panel extended to the portrayal of the Tuesday meeting","depth":8},{"id":225,"text":"attended by Holder , Issa , Cummings and others .","depth":8},{"id":226,"text":"Issa and Republicans rejected the conditions of Holder 's offer ,","depth":8},{"id":227,"text":"while Cummings and Democrats said","depth":9},{"id":228,"text":"the panel should work with Holder","depth":10},{"id":229,"text":"to seek a resolution .","depth":10},{"id":230,"text":"Issa said","depth":9},{"id":231,"text":"he was surprised by Obama 's action","depth":10},{"id":232,"text":"and questioned","depth":11},{"id":233,"text":"whether the White House 's role in Fast and Furious `` has been greater","depth":12},{"id":234,"text":"than previously acknowledged . ''","depth":12},{"id":235,"text":"Sen. Charles Grassley of Iowa , the ranking Republican member of the Senate Judiciary Committee , told CNN","depth":11},{"id":236,"text":"he previously traced the program only up to the level of an assistant attorney general .","depth":11},{"id":237,"text":"`` Now it raises the question","depth":12},{"id":238,"text":"of what does the president know","depth":13},{"id":239,"text":"and when did he know it by the claim of executive privilege , ''","depth":13},{"id":240,"text":"said Grassley ,","depth":12},{"id":241,"text":"who participated in Tuesday 's meeting .","depth":12},{"id":242,"text":"But Carl Tobias , professor at the University of Richmond 's School of Law , said","depth":11},{"id":243,"text":"it does not appear Obama was involved with the Fast and Furious program .","depth":11},{"id":244,"text":"`` He is trying to protect the prerogatives of the department and the people","depth":12},{"id":245,"text":"who work for him , ''","depth":12},{"id":246,"text":"Tobias said of the executive privilege .","depth":11},{"id":247,"text":"CNN senior legal analyst Jeffrey Toobin said","depth":9},{"id":248,"text":"that","depth":10},{"id":249,"text":"while Holder may be embarrassed ,","depth":11},{"id":250,"text":"he wo n't ultimately be found in contempt .","depth":11},{"id":251,"text":"`` This is going to be just another political dispute , ''","depth":10},{"id":252,"text":"Toobin told CNN 's Anderson Cooper .","depth":10},{"id":253,"text":"`` If people remember at all ,","depth":11},{"id":254,"text":"they 'll remember","depth":11},{"id":255,"text":"23 Republicans were for it ,","depth":11},{"id":256,"text":"17 Democrats were against it . ''","depth":11}],"relations":[{"parent":513,"left":0,"right":512,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":512,"left":407,"right":511,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":407,"left":373,"right":406,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":373,"left":262,"right":372,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":262,"left":260,"right":261,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":260,"left":258,"right":259,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":258,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":259,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":261,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":372,"left":289,"right":371,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":289,"left":272,"right":288,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":272,"left":266,"right":271,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":266,"left":263,"right":265,"relation":"at